      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Localita'                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-age-loc-age       to   w-let-arc-age-loc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Mnemonico                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
