      *                      * Nome                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-age-nom      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ragione sociale                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-age-rag      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Via                                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-age-via      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Localita'                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-age-loc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Mnemonico                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-age-mne      .
